1.9
log
@new MULTI_PACKAGES
@
text
@This is the IMAP4rev1 server from the University of Washington.
Included are backwards-compatible (almost) POP2 and POP3 servers.

	ipop2d		POP2 daemon
	ipop3d		POP3 daemon
	imapd		IMAP4rev1 daemon

Flavors

	plaintext	Enable unencrypted plaintext passwords
@


